        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This weathered crook is often carried by chaplains of more primal deities. The carved wooden shaft bears the marks of fire damage and smells of campfire meals past. It counts as a wooden religious symbol for deities who grant the nature domain. While traveling in exploration mode, you and your allies within 120 feet count anyone\u2019s travel Speed of 15 feet or lower as 25 feet.",
